  <brief_title>NO Donors and Inhibitors to Study Imbalance of Nitrogen Stress and Antioxidant Defense in COPD</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double Blind, Crossover Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate the Effect of L-arginine and Aminoguanidine on Bronchial and Alveolar Nitric Oxide and Nitric Oxide Metabolites in Exhaled Air, Breath Condensate, Nasal Lavage, Mouth Wash Fluid, and Induced Sputum in 7 Healthy Non-smokers, 10 Smokers and 12 COPD Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
